title: The Fugitive S02E22 Moon Child DivX
description:
The Fugitive

S02E22
Moon Child

Original Air Date: 16 February 1965

-One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
-Remastered audio and video from VHS
-Includes the original orchestral music score

Kimble (David Janssen) walks into a hotbed of suspicion when he befriends a mentally-impaired young woman in a town where several women have been murdered.

Joanne: June Harding. Starling: Murray Hamilton. Alma: Virginia Christine. Sheriff: David Sheiner. Randy: (Harry) Dean Stanton.
